text: Nutbush may refer to: *Nutbush, Tennessee, a town in Haywood County, childhood home of singer Tina Turner *Nutbush Township, Warren County, North Carolina, one of twelve townships in Warren County, North Carolina *Nutbush, Memphis, a district of Memphis, Tennessee *"Nutbush City Limits", a song about Nutbush, Tennessee by singer Tina Turner **The Nutbush, a dance categorized as a Line dance, performed to the song Nutbush City Limits
title: Nutbush
